103
00:04:37,396 --> 00:04:38,973
83% in Kargil,

104
00:04:38,973 --> 00:04:42,271
and in some areas it is as high as 99%.

105
00:04:42,271 --> 00:04:43,669
The third and the biggest reason,

106
00:04:43,669 --> 00:04:47,031
the 6th Schedule will give the people
of Ladakh their democratic rights.

107
